features: Eye-Caring and Energy-Saving: Our desk lamp is constructed with a 45° beam angle design, reducing 30% screen glare than other lamps. Fundamentally relieve eye fatigue caused by long-time watching computer screens with no direct light to your eyes. The desk light has 60 high quality LED units that give off uniform illumination in a wide lighting range, while consuming 80% less energy than incandescent lamps.

Easy Control and Cord Management: Without an annoying cord hanging from the lamp, this table lamp can be easily controlled by the integrated touch buttons on the lamp. Our desktop lamp features a power-on memory function, which conveniently resumes your last selected light color and brightness before it was turned off.

3 Color Selectable with Continuous Dimming: This dimmable desk clip lamp offers 3 color temperature options (3000K warm, 4000K neutral, 6000K cool white). Each light color enables continuous dimming from 10%-100% brightness, ideal for reading, studying, working, crafting, sewing, gaming, etc.

360°Flexible Gooseneck: The 360° adjustable gooseneck tube allows you to position the office lamp at the exact height you need (maximum lamp height: 30 inches), perfect for 15-29 inch monitors. Made with high-quality silicone and metal materials, this gooseneck desk lamp can bend up to 100,000 times without breaking. The clamp lamp has a silicone pad to prevent scratching the table.

USB Power Adapter Included: The package includes: 1x Eye-caring Desk Lamp, 1x Metal Clamp, 1x Power Adapter(5V/2.4A), 1x User Manual. You can power the lamp via the adapter or from your power bank, computer, and more. Our energy-saving LED desk lamp has higher brightness and better heat dissipation, longer service life, no need to be replaced frequently.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Impressed by the quality and light pattern
reviews.reviewText: I needed a desk lamp that would illuminate my desk, preventing eye strain while writing while using my PC. So far, I am very satisfied with the lamp.The lamp boasts high build quality, with its body almost entirely made of metal. The gooseneck is firm, holding its position, and the touch controls are intuitive and responsive.For those using it with a monitor, the most crucial feature is the asymmetric light pattern. I compared the SUPERDANNY lamp to other gooseneck desk lamps without this feature and am impressed by the light pattern. No direct light hits my eyes, and glare on the monitor is minimal, even though the lamp illuminates a large area of the desk. I've included a picture that shows the light pattern. The color temperatures and brightness controls are as advertised.The mounting clamp is very low-profile, allowing only a few millimeters of gap if pushed against a wall. The clamp is padded on both sides to prevent marring of the desk surface, although the padding on the bottom side seems minimal. For those with very expensive desks, felt tape or cloth can be used as extra padding.The lamp is an extremely good value at $30 and occasionally $20 on sale. For the money, I couldn't be happier. Only time will tell whether the LEDs will last on the lamp, but based on my impression of the product, I have a feeling that they will.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for WFH setups!
reviews.reviewText: This fit perfectly on my standing desk! I have two monitors and have it set up between them. The light is solid/ bright enough to hover both monitors and the keyboard. If you are debating on getting one or two, one does the job. I would get two if you have a desk longer than 47inch L. Setting it up is easy. Switching to different light modes is finicky/I must press hard; I mostly leave it on the bright setting.
